title: Earth Therapeutics Body Sponge, Anti-Bacterial, 1 Count

This revolutionary barrier prevents the growth of bacteria on the sponge even before it has a chance to settle. So there is no transfer of impurities from one washing to the next. Each cleansing begins with a fresh slate. Germ- proof your cleansing regimen. With every day use, anti-bacterial benefits last for 3 months. For best results, replace with a new sponge after this period. Product of Japan.
